{"tid":750360,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"越正面就越好運 越負面就越黑仔","createTime":"2018-07-20T21:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T00:10:31.000Z","uid":193407,"like":367,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"661484f388d9e50e3df40b1278815fb77a055845","tid":750360,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:09:25.000Z","msg":"如題 雖然唔會成日都係咁 但有冇人有同感？<br />\n<br />\n自己分享下先<br />\n<br />\n之前有日個人勁負勁頹 心情好差 嗰日落雨 我嘅繪圖板壞咗要去維修 我一手拎住盒嘢,一手擔住遮 因為就嚟刪舖所以謂有跑過去 加上焗到爆 成個人勁狼狽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到去間嘢話要整一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時仲要係有樣嘢要急住畫 聽到要整一個月即刻負能量爆燈 然後走之後唔記得拎返把遮 又要跑返上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞成身汗痴笠笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都算 重點嚟喇 一邊揾梗個巴士站起邊 一邊用手機google map嘅我自然冇留意地下 一嘢踩咗落去<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;咦 扁patpat 軟林林嘅？笠咖喎...&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n係啊 踩屎啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好撚黑仔 但諗嘢正面嗰陣就唔會發生呢啲事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正面嘅時候會有啲小幸運發生 試過第一次去新地方完全冇盪失路 一去就揾到,搭小巴冇散銀俾錢個司機話唔洗俾etc...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實可唔可以用科學嚟解釋到？例如磁場 氣場嗰啲乜乜物物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f3dd734322cfb9fc4c7dfd584baaf2749a4138","tid":750360,"uid":88491,"like":134,"dislike":46,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T21:12:19.000Z","msg":"吸引力法則"},{"pid":"5ddfe8565a436303b683cc8704ff7dd4e0225a57","tid":750360,"uid":54226,"like":166,"dislike":7,"score":159,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:01:05.000Z","msg":"咁啱得咁橋"},{"pid":"9b04217f810212d47866a1c622a58fcea708035d","tid":750360,"uid":13835,"like":220,"dislike":6,"score":214,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:02:25.000Z","msg":"調返轉<br />\n個人越攰運氣越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打麻雀好精神就出沖<br />\n一攰就食糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早幾日感冒跟住就抽籤抽中左好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fab9ed0fed5a68d3e61b5f8c329c1fd2764683","tid":750360,"uid":77473,"like":686,"dislike":11,"score":675,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:03:08.000Z","msg":"覺得自已黑仔嘅人只會留意黑仔嘢去証明自已黑仔<br />\n<br />\n覺得只已好運嘅人只會留意好運嘢圦証明自已好運"},{"pid":"fd7577934c2e33e09d3a3f8c99369f7a5454288f","tid":750360,"uid":190713,"like":136,"dislike":6,"score":130,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:04:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得打得飛機多會黑仔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c944294a219a93198a8400df2a6feccbf07f74","tid":750360,"uid":14901,"like":230,"dislike":1,"score":229,"quote":{"pid":"fd7577934c2e33e09d3a3f8c99369f7a5454288f","tid":750360,"uid":190713,"like":136,"dislike":6,"score":130,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:04:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得打得飛機多會黑仔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:06:21.000Z","msg":"仆你個街我一打完飛機上連登就見到你呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901177c3225aeb651166ecbcc1e0ecdb9699c166","tid":750360,"uid":132587,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:34:51.000Z","msg":"正面果陣落雨覺得好浪漫 <br />\n負面果陣覺得落雨個天好黑 好煩 落完雨有彩虹 心諗d人影乜鳩 係咪成世人未見過"},{"pid":"218af8ffd3dc5ddbb91abf5f1563fff4bf00fca4","tid":750360,"uid":176318,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:35: