gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T22:06:21.000Z","msg":"仆你個街我一打完飛機上連登就見到你呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T03:17:18.000Z","msg":"咁早打飛機？"},{"pid":"e580278d785d0ef7d9141dae5ed407123b452c9b","tid":750360,"uid":29238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"唔好追求咩解釋啦 <br />\n用經驗去行事就得啦<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得個人正面左會帶黎好運<br />\n咁多d關注身邊正面既事同人 同自己情緒<br />\n大家開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe1a377a399dc42fc1815c18293968c900295c3","tid":750360,"uid":121409,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"你心情唔好咪會自動將啲衰嘢放大同記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心情好你明明落雨淋到狗咁都可以覺得好有feel好爽好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814e09622b5b1f2b0b00d171bad66b531bf26789","tid":750360,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T03:24:33.000Z","msg":"Maybe 正面未必帶到好運 但負面就必定黑仔"},{"pid":"7fff73a8dffe6eca57b401a953b560679a472563","tid":750360,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"進化論話你知負面情緒有用，<br />\n睇你識唔識運用控制，<br />\n唔好乜都屈負面情緒<br />\n好無辜㗎"},{"pid":"119b821da5a83fb4e8dc6e5331b45cb7be4535d5","tid":750360,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"我絕對係咁<br />\n所以而家都盡量平常心"},{"pid":"684f50835209e8a5a29412d95b3a6b7cc60b81d9","tid":750360,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ac37f0339b2f1782b2f9d86ab97232122404d9","tid":750360,"uid":2